Package: actuarial.ifrs9r
Type: Package
Title: IFRS 9 Expected Credit Loss Modelling with Transition Matrices
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Your", family = "Name", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "you@example.com"))
Description: Tools to compute IFRS 9 Expected Credit Losses (ECL) using transition matrices, staging, scenario weighting, EAD/LGD modelling, and discounting. Includes utilities to validate transition matrices and derive lifetime probability of default (PD) term structures. Supports exporting results to Excel.
